data.description: Have you been searching for a home with some extra “wow” factor? If so, this is one you won’t want to miss! This lovely 3 bed / 2 bath home has 1,823 sqft of well laid-out living space, and sits on a spacious .31 acre lot in Paragould.   Stepping through the front door you will be greeted first by a beautiful and inviting living room with a large window that fills the space with warm, natural light. Continuing forward you will find a stunning kitchen and dining area that would stun your next dinner party guests. The dining area is roomy, with plenty of natural light, and complete with a lovely woodburning stove & accent wall and modern light fixture which contrasts beautifully to create a delightfully warm & timeless atmosphere. Looking to the left you will notice how this beautiful aesthetic flows seamlessly into the vast, open kitchen with ample counter space, gorgeous granite countertops and wood cabinets. Continuing through the doors in the kitchen you will be surprised by the cavernously large pantry which leads to the laundry room and a stunningly large bonus room beautifully accented by a large bay window overlooking the front yard.
